## **Summary**
This data was from 1,559 individual U.S. adult citizens who was surveyed about the who they are likely to vote for in the 2024 Elections, conducted in March 10-12 2024 by YouGov, which we seek to determine what proportion of all votes will be cast for Joe Biden in the 2024 Elections.
